snippet.title: Jumpstart Reading for 1st Grade Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Jumpstart Reading for 1st Grade Full Playthrough

Jumpstart Reading for 1st Grade Full Playthrough  is a JumpStart game released by Knowledge Adventure in 1997 that focuses on teaching language arts at the 1st grade curriculum.
